&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;-- textDocument/codeAction can return either Command[] or CodeAction[]. If it&lt;/span&gt;
